17:47.790 --> 17:48.270
Saya...

17:49.160 --> 17:50.920
Saya pun belum fikir apa-apa lagi.

17:50.920 --> 17:52.350
Satu-satunya kelebihan kita

17:52.350 --> 17:54.440
